Titolo: Master of Epic

Anno: 2005

Descrizione: Master of Epic is a free Japanese MMORPG. It has not been released outside of Japan. It was adapted into an anime (Master of Epic: The Animation Age) by Gonzo and Palm Studio, and aired on TV Tokyo in 2007. Master of Epic does not have levels, and instead the player has a range of skills, such as strength, clubs, magics, and business, which level up through use. Titles are earned when certain skills or combinations of skills reach certain ranks. Players are able to select between four races for player characters, and can play the game in four separate historical periods, known as Ages.